---
import Landing from "../layouts/Landing.astro";
import { DOWNLOAD_URL } from "../config";
---

<Landing
  title="Thanks for buying Drobu"
  description="Thanks for buying Drobu. Your license key is on its way to your email."
>
  <main class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-24">
    <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto text-center">
      <img
        src="/drobule.png"
        alt="Drobu mascot"
        width="80"
        height="80"
        class="mx-auto mb-8"
      />

      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">
        Thanks for buying Drobu!
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary mb-10">
        Your license key is on its way to your email. A receipt from Stripe should already be in your inbox.
      </p>

      <div class="text-left bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8 text-sm text-text-secondary space-y-3">
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-text-primary mb-3">What happens next</h2>
        <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2">
          <li>You'll get an email with your license key shortly. Early customers get manually-issued keys, so allow a few hours.</li>
          <li>If Drobu is already running, open <strong class="text-text-primary">Settings &rarr; License</strong>, paste the key, and click <strong class="text-text-primary">Activate</strong>.</li>
          <li>If your free trial has already expired, opening the Drobu hotkey now brings up an activation prompt — paste the key right there.</li>
        </ol>

        <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-white/5">
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            <strong class="text-text-secondary">Haven't installed Drobu yet?</strong>
            <a href={DOWNLOAD_URL} download="Drobu.dmg" class="text-accent hover:underline">Download the DMG</a>,
            drag it to your Applications folder, then launch Drobu. Paste your license key when the activation prompt appears.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-3">
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            <strong class="text-text-secondary">Didn't get an email after 24 hours?</strong>
            Email <a href="mailto:support@drobu.app" class="text-accent hover:underline">support@drobu.app</a> with your Stripe receipt and we'll get your key out right away.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 text-sm text-text-muted">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-text-secondary transition-colors">Back to home</a>
        <span>&middot;</span>
        <a href="/terms" class="hover:text-text-secondary transition-colors">Terms</a>
        <span>&middot;</span>
        <a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-text-secondary transition-colors">Privacy</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Landing>
